{"tid":1356064,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"唔好再比較咩上環同元朗邊個重要d","createTime":"2019-07-23T12:08:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-23T13:29:38.000Z","uid":103861,"like":27,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"903683e6fe2ec95170b7ca87ca93e74aec8dc492","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:08:41.000Z","msg":"屌你唔好再分化<br />\n兩邊都同樣重要<br />\n係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">同樣重要</span>呀屌你<br />\n<br />\n唔好比較<br />\n冇嘢值得比較<br />\n2樣都係香港人重視嘅核心價值<br />\n唔好再用d咩「spin」呀「耍走」呀「中晒圈套」呢d字眼<br />\n5大訴求重要 義士安全重要<br />\n大西北安全都重要 香港唔要白色恐怖<br />\n<br />\n冇人係condom<br />\n全部都一撚樣咁重要<br />\n<br />\n元朗單野第一次發生<br />\n引發嘅聲音好大係好正常<br />\n大家呢兩日擺多咗注意力落元朗係好正常<br />\n唔代表大家唔知上環咩事<br />\n<br />\n同樣地<br />\n有時推多咗上環po都唔代表大西北義士係condom<br />\n<br />\n下晝何妖祖墳單野一多幾個po大家又開始互屌<br />\n真係唔好咁緊張咁激動先<br />\n其實大家點會唔知最終目標係政府啫？<br />\n幾個鐘頭 俾大家開心下<br />\n真係喂威喂太耐失晒焦先屌啦好嘛<br />\n<br />\n唔好分化<br />\n唔好因為見到另一邊多幾個po就灰晒機<br />\n相信同路人<br />\n相信一直以嚟陪你走到呢度嘅人<br />\n我地有良知有義氣<br />\n<br />\n元朗係緊急事態 係無差別襲擊<br />\n係首次咁明目張膽嘅官黑勾結<br />\n大家冇呢個心理準備<br />\n亦都冇經驗處理同黑社會有關嘅衝突<br />\n所以元朗嘅事先會多po喺度傾<br />\n等元朗嘅事處理一下<br />\n上環嗰邊同樣都有人一直關注<br />\n有人整合 有人搞聯署 有人搞文宣<br />\n<br />\n一齊努力啦好嘛？<br />\n<br />\n不篤灰 不割席 不分化"},{"pid":"21f0cca5d5d4d7d521ee22ed77d03bddb8f1be3a","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:12:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8063a3379db7f083513da8c1525435e10792330c","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:12:34.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1f1cea58b932fba79090ce3e5f4fd8883d6871c9","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:12:45.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6d6e78a44bcd0e1403442ab6c678c2859635aca3","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:13:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"414287ac31f86e5bfbf97e4922802f3ce90a6943","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:14:14.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"86f489a86852bb5aaeb78e640252fb0c83f0c48f","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:14:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"669dabc7fd45cf14655ca8e89ae0e8341613c1d4","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:15:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1c2b32af862253373a0b07506a4a346504affed3","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:18:54.000Z","msg":"整合後的 5 大訴求<br />\n1. 全面撤回送中條例<br />\n2. 撤銷<span style=\"color: red;\">6.12</span>暴動定性<br />\n3. 釋放被捕義士並承諾永不追究<br />\n4. 全面實行雙普選<br />\n5. 成立獨立調查委員會，追究黑警濫用暴力，<span style=\"color: red;\">徹查警黑勾結7.21元朗恐襲</span>"},{"pid":"67664687245b7c209e9b149bd14769e5a7e5d98e","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:19:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f13c15d7950da5b21918a2a4583c998e3302b5f2","tid":1356064,"uid":71092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:20:05.000Z","msg":"Right"},{"pid":"b9a1fa18a91667e5dc27f531f42040c38a0f11bf","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:21:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29ade16c1b08f34f98012ca2a5cdd34f98934383","tid":1356064,"uid":55493,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:22:11.000Z","msg":"推呀推"},{"pid":"cc9f4e73f987eaf655fb90b7a2bde82da191186c","tid":1356064,"uid":53915,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T12:35:51.000Z","msg":"搞元朗同上環事件冇衝突 唔應該分先後<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1356031\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1356031</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ac99e4081882ad3d61109be201872a9581e446eb","tid":1356064,"uid":103861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-23T13:12:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d7a679bcd468e957332a0d2ad1f048db571a2e1